divs: Sighting DetailsI was at restaurant , sitting by water with a friend. Some dolphines were feeding so I got up and took 7 pictures. Went back and sat down . I looked at pictures and in 6of the 7 pics there appears to be a half moon. Then there is a teardrop cloud going near it. The in other photo a pink circle and a pink cone surround half moon. It moves to the left of the sun, then above the sun then to right of sun. I had stopped taking pics cause dolphines were done feeding. Theses pics were all at 6:42 pm. There is no moon visable. Went and took another pic at 6:46 pm. There is something there. And I did not use a flash.
Summary: i took some pictures of dolphines. . when i looked at pics 6 of the pics have something in sky
